---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-12 text-center" transition:animate="fade">
      <h1 class="text-5xl mb-4">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
        A little bit about who I am
      </p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none" transition:animate="fade">
      <p>
        Hi, I'm Wesley Deland. I'm a software engineer based in Texas. I build things with code - sometimes for work, sometimes for fun.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What I Do</h2>
      
      <ul>
        <li>Full-stack development</li>
        <li>Cloud infrastructure</li>
        <li>Automation and tooling</li>
        <li>Breaking things and fixing them</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Tech I Use</h2>
      
      <p>
        I work with a variety of tools and technologies including 
        <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">C#</a>, 
        <a href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">.NET</a>, 
        <a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Azure</a>, 
        <a href="https://angular.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Angular</a>, 
        <a href="https://typescriptlang.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TypeScript</a>, 
        <a href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/apps/aspnet/blazor" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Blazor</a>, 
        <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/sql-server/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SQL Server</a>, and 
        <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a>.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      
      <p>
        Find me on <a href="https://github.com/wesleydeland">GitHub</a>, 
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jamesdeland">LinkedIn</a>, or 
        send me an email at <a href="mailto:mail@wesleydeland.com">mail@wesleydeland.com</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Check out the <a href="/blog/journal">Journal</a> to see what I've been writing about.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>